---
import founder1 from "../assets/founder-1.png";
---

<section class="bg-[#FAF7F2] py-20 sm:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl items-center gap-12 px-5 sm:px-6 lg:grid-cols-[0.95fr_1.05fr] lg:gap-16">
    <div>
      <img
        src={founder1.src}
        alt="Aravind Kumar"
        class="h-[520px] w-full rounded-[2rem] object-cover sm:h-[680px] lg:rounded-[3rem]"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl lg:pl-4">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[#D97706] sm:text-sm">
        A Letter From Our Founder
      </p>

      <blockquote class="mt-8">
        <p class="text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-[#1F2937] sm:text-5xl sm:leading-tight lg:text-6xl">
          &ldquo;When we started Children First, we did not begin with a strategy.
          We began with a question.
          What happens when a child is full of potential but lacks opportunity?&rdquo;
        </p>
      </blockquote>

      <div class="mt-10 border-t border-[#1F2937]/15 pt-8">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1F2937]">
          Aravind Kumar
        </p>

        <p class="mt-2 text-lg text-[#1F2937]/65">
          Founder
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
